'''Kontag''' was an important group in refitting [[Starship/Legends|starships]] with additional security systems during the days of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. The headquarters was located on [[Pirin]]. Nearing its end, about a [[Standard decade/Legends|decade]] before the [[Invasion of Naboo/Legends|Invasion of Naboo]], its executives made a deal with [[Lorian Nod]] to save them from bankruptcy by creating a false necessity among Old Republic [[Senator/Legends|Senators]] for augmented security systems. By accessing Nod's cheap labor pool of [[Youngling/Legends|children]], the company saved itself until the untimely arrival and investigation of [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Dooku/Legends|Dooku]] and his [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]].

